{% extends "layouts/base.njk" %}

{% block content %}
<section class="services-grid">
  <article class="card service-card">
    <h3>Editorial strategy</h3>
    <p>Advisory work for institutions that need coherent long-form editorial positioning, publishing strategy, or public-facing narrative discipline.</p>
    <ul class="check-list">
      <li>Editorial architecture and publishing programs</li>
      <li>Message discipline for serious organizations</li>
      <li>Decision support for complex editorial choices</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
  <article class="card service-card">
    <h3>Ontology and knowledge design</h3>
    <p>Structured knowledge modeling for projects that need traceable definitions, explicit relationships, and auditable reasoning surfaces.</p>
    <ul class="check-list">
      <li>Ontology design and taxonomy work</li>
      <li>Knowledge graph and semantic modeling advisory</li>
      <li>Schema strategy for high-consequence systems</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
  <article class="card service-card">
    <h3>Decision-intelligence systems</h3>
    <p>Design and review for explainable workflows where accountability, provenance, and governance matter more than novelty alone.</p>
    <ul class="check-list">
      <li>Auditable AI workflows</li>
      <li>Risk-aware decision support</li>
      <li>Governance and review structures</li>
    </ul>
  </article>
  <article class="card service-card">
    <h3>Engagement model</h3>
    <p>Services are selective and scoped deliberately. Use contact to describe the institution, the decision environment, and the outcome required.</p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="button-secondary" href="contact.html">Discuss a project</a>
    </div>
  </article>
</section>
{% endblock %}
